quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  6,9,"Walaw jaAAalnahu malakan lajaAAalnahurajulan walalabasna AAalayhim ma yalbisoon"
  6,10,"Walaqadi istuhzi-a birusulin min qablika fahaqabillatheena sakhiroo minhum ma kanoobihi yastahzi-oon"
  6,11,"Qul seeroo fee al-ardi thumma onthurookayfa kana AAaqibatu almukaththibeen"
  6,12,"Qul liman ma fee assamawatiwal-ardi qul lillahi kataba AAalanafsihi arrahmata layajmaAAannakum ilayawmi alqiyamati la rayba feehi allatheenakhasiroo anfusahum fahum la yu/minoon"
  6,13,"Walahu ma sakana fee allayli wannahariwahuwa assameeAAu alAAaleem"
  6,14,"Qul aghayra Allahi attakhithuwaliyyan fatiri assamawati wal-ardiwahuwa yutAAimu wala yutAAamu qul inneeomirtu an akoona awwala man aslama wala takoonanna minaalmushrikeen"
  6,15,"Qul innee akhafu in AAasayturabbee AAathaba yawmin AAatheem"
  6,16,"Man yusraf AAanhu yawma-ithinfaqad rahimahu wathalika alfawzu almubeen"
  6,17,"Wa-in yamsaska Allahu bidurrinfala kashifa lahu illa huwa wa-in yamsaskabikhayrin fahuwa AAala kulli shay-in qadeer"
  6,18,"Wahuwa alqahiru fawqa AAibadihiwahuwa alhakeemu alkhabeer"
